You can add a short explanation that summarizes your
editing changes in the input field provided. This is
completely optional.

Mouse over the Save button at any time to reveal the
summary input and type in your text. Hitting Enter
will save the page.

The Page Summary will show up in various places
including the Page Revision History and any listings
where the page is shown.

If you want to save the page with no summary, simply
click Save.
